The bottle contains some wine.

> x jar
The jar is empty.

> ; ==============================================================================
> ; THE 'FILL WITH' BUG!
> ; ==============================================================================
> ; Now we attempt to fill the jar with wine (it will fail by default):
> fill jar with wine
You can't fill the jar with the wine.

> x bottle
The bottle contains some wine.

> x jar
The jar is empty.

> pour wine
(taking the bottle of wine first)
You pour the wine on the ground.

